{"tid":1600553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隱世醫療室上線啦！","createTime":"2019-09-28T16:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:16:22.000Z","uid":267240,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"23589ffec8a233dbb54677b1ed49dbf5ff95d49f","tid":1600553,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">隱世醫療室上線啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nP牌唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手動轉！<br />\n    <br />\n有見於市民礙於對個人資料洩露之擔憂或經濟困難未能到醫院求診，一些醫護人員設立了非緊急醫療支援Telegram熱線，已接觸超過200個病者。「隱世醫療室」安排如下：<br />\n<br />\n▪<span style=\"color: gold;\">無需提供個人資料<br />\n▪於Telegram解答醫學問題，並會根據急切性於24小時內解答<br />\n▪若有需要將安排義務會診<br />\n▪核心團隊：急症、內科、骨科、婦產、眼科、和放射科醫生 <br />\n▪亦有提供：傷口護理、精神科、Xray 轉介支援作進一步檢查</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>*Telegram: @hidden_clinic*</strong></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n另外收到不少有心人的查詢，在此簡單回答<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 有關人手支援及藥物捐贈</span></span><br />\n答: 我們暫時人手足夠，所以大家可以先協助其他更有需要的機構。另外，為確保藥物及醫療用品的品質，所有用品均購自註冊藥房，暫不接受醫療用品捐贈，敬請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 有關會否選擇性診治個案</span></span><br />\n答: 我們遵循人道援助的原則，會基於人們的需要，無分種族、宗教、性別或政治連繫提供援助<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 有關收費及回覆速度</span></span><br />\n答: 我們的服務屬義務性質，費用全免。惟所有醫護義工也是以工餘時間提供支援，因此不能確保能夠解答所有問題，但定必盡力協助大家。若24小時仍未回覆，請重發問題。<br />\n<br />\n我們都一直在學習，希望大家在不同崗位上一同為病人努力，共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港加油。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad24a4ef835cbaa5645ae344c0824c21eb83c3c3","tid":1600553,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"a1f65faa051b5847feab33f1cfd19ffd1aa2d04b","tid":1600553,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n入黎投票呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「光 復 香 港」  廢 除 《 聯 合 聲 明 》 第 三 次 公 投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600396</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2fcff194929d12aed41e29154bb7a17a8907117","tid":1600553,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"f69d96763084bb8b183a201cf701e5c09784d4fb","tid":1600553,"uid":246158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8eed738472ff0887a1979d4b239c4e38d588169b","tid":1600553,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"559b7e37ca3c080522a1d7dba7a5adbe627fad60","tid":1600553,"uid":59363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"有心<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"65feb9d09da1a63d52d23b180fd329a3decad5a2","tid":1600553,"uid":196771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d0fe5c128f43bea0f18e4f608389fede57031c","tid":1600553,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"865d8f1335fbde029ca0cacf18d90cf32aa477e9","tid":1600553,"uid":290977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"善舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f0e3fa349adcb7427a13bed5f36a51a8cfb084","tid":1600553,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2e8e65cc4cd958511040074fe3f7342e0119bf1","tid":1600553,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"64ea653ad44be1946b